## Key Measures (DAX)

| Measure | Formula Logic |
|---|---|
| Collection Rate | Paid / Billed |
| Balance | Billed - Paid - Adjustment - Dedcop |
| Active Users | Count of users with Billed > 0 |
| Avg Attorney Fee | Total Attorney Fee / Count of Attorneys |
